AEGEAN SEA.
DNC 09.
AN EARTHQUAKE OCCURRED AT 202231Z JUL WITH A
PRELIMINARY MAGNITUDE OF 6.8, IN 36-59N 27-34E.
A TSUNAMI MAY HAVE BEEN GENERATED. TSUNAMI WAVES
ARE POSSIBLE ALONG SOME COASTS. TSUNAMI WAVE
HEIGHTS CANNOT BE PREDICTED AND MAY BE A
SERIES OF WAVES WHICH COULD BE DANGEROUS FOR
SEVERAL HOURS AFTER THE INITIAL WAVE ARRIVAL.
